{"tid":2493837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日自衞隊角色加重 走火風險增","createTime":"2021-04-18T08:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:04:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ede27ba81d5c0c235aca8aafc943ae5105d2fae","tid":2493837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210418/36BQF7D3ZZDUFFKRKA57ATTVLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2F36BQF7D3ZZDUFFKRKA57ATTVLI%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RIcyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=1c8e764b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2F36BQF7D3ZZDUFFKRKA57ATTVLI%2F&h=d2371000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210418/36BQF7D3ZZDUFFKRKA57ATTVLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n日自衞隊角色加重 走火風險增<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lrmdDc2upXQs-ATfRr5aH44Wmow=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KHEKYVXIFFBJNP4B6AHLRVUAWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlrmdDc2upXQs-ATfRr5aH44Wmow%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKHEKYVXIFFBJNP4B6AHLRVUAWY.jpg&h=81afba30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■海上自衞隊艦艇或可通過台海維護區域安全。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國與日本52年來首次明確地在聯合聲明中明確提及台灣，日媒認為日本今後在維持台海穩定的角色更大，但專家憂慮區內爆發衝突的機會因此增加。<br />\n<br />\n日本產經新聞報道，美日峯會對於台海和平穩定的重要性達成一致看法，日本扮演的角色將變得更重，並指政府內部有人提案，海上自衞隊艦艇將來可通過台灣海峽，與以美國為主的國家一同對中國施壓。<br />\n<br />\n美軍一旦介入涉台灣的戰事，駐日美軍基地等可能成為解放軍攻擊的對象。報道引述高官表示，若政府認定這屬於武力攻擊，或可出動自衞隊應對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者憂中日關係趨惡化<br />\n<br />\n另外，中山大學中國與亞太區域研究所教授郭育仁認為，美日為盟國，共同聲明屬硬性文件，具強制力，因此前日的聲明可視為美日同盟的補充追加文件，將同盟安全防護範圍擴至台海。<br />\n<br />\n不過，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"a809e184a15f2e28999553e3f5c37527f9a7e1d4","tid":2493837,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國幾時先可以復國"},{"pid":"e01983c379b1c9db490e5667f5caa15e01c41f48","tid":2493837,"uid":259716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"修改憲法第9條先啦。"},{"pid":"a330d0d60ae2248195ce3412f7758585cd22fca0","tid":2493837,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbd2b8ca5567383ba41be9636510fd1ab8c9da6","tid":2493837,"uid":209662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大日本帝國萬歲"},{"pid":"d88eeb2f2f810d78f8c081ba1facfb93f65d2ce2","tid":2493837,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a809e184a15f2e28999553e3f5c37527f9a7e1d4","tid":2493837,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國幾時先可以復國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"最基本要解決國內少子化問題同經濟停滯先 大家必須要預我哋嘅生活方式一定會冇"},{"pid":"1299098a873569f01e634c20ef4c2e4b7223e837","tid":2493837,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"頑張れ、日本"},{"pid":"8d8727368be31dcf1bac9516be358a705efcbbf1","tid":2493837,"uid":266892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"無実のシナ人は一人も居らん！"},{"pid":"77e0f3161333be4e58c284697180ae69153a8466","tid":2493837,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚容易走火咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee881aaaf4320552dd5eaeda3ea3ef2705e7895","tid":2493837,"uid